Package com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.embed

Class Embed.Builder

java.lang.Object
com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.embed.Embed.Builder
Enclosing class:
Embed
public static class Embed.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
The Builder class allows for easy creation of an Embed Object. Make sure to read the wiki page on our GitHub to understand how to use this effectively. (https://github.com/ItsRadiiX/Definity-Webhooks/wiki)
